src=\"/static/38559bf115772b6b51880856fd1c88f9/d318f/gatsby-remark-vscode__ts.png\"\n            alt=\"Gatsby Remark VS Code (TypeScript preview)\"\n            title=\"Gatsby Remark VS Code (TypeScript preview)\"\n            loading=\"lazy\"\n            decoding=\"async\"\n            style=\"width:100%;height:100%;margin:0;vertical-align:middle;position:absolute;top:0;left:0;\"\n          />\n        </picture>\n  </a>\n    </span></p>\n<h3>JavaScript Preview</h3>\n<p><span\n      class=\"gatsby-resp-image-wrapper\"\n      style=\"position: relative; display: block; margin-left: auto; margin-right: auto; max-width: 1405px; \"\n    >\n      <a\n    class=\"gatsby-resp-image-link\"\n    href=\"/static/cfbed43c12c620eeb99d6ab9a05bfb6f/b30aa/gatsby-remark-vscode__js.png\"\n    style=\"display: block\"\n    target=\"_blank\"\n    rel=\"noopener\"\n  >\n    <span\n    class=\"gatsby-resp-image-background-image\"\n    style=\"padding-bottom: 30.859375%; position: relative; bottom: 0; left: 0; background-image: url('data:image/svg+xml,%3csvg%20xmlns=\\'http://www.w3.org/2000/svg\\'%20width=\\'400\\'%20height=\\'123\\'%20viewBox=\\'0%200%20400%20123\\'%20preserveAspectRatio=\\'none\\'%3e%3cpath%20d=\\'M10%2011c-2%201-2%207-2%2050v49l2%201c4%203%20375%203%20379%200l2-1V61c0-43%200-49-2-50-2-3-377-3-379%200\\'%20fill=\\'%23d3d3d3\\'%20fill-rule=\\'evenodd\\'/%3e%3c/svg%3e'); background-size: cover; display: block;\"\n  ></span>\n  <picture>\n          <source\n              srcset=\"/static/cfbed43c12c620eeb99d6ab9a05bfb6f/bd5dd/gatsby-remark-vscode__js.webp 512w,\n/static/cfbed43c12c620eeb99d6ab9a05bfb6f/a9a89/gatsby-remark-vscode__js.webp 1024w,\n/static/cfbed43c12c620eeb99d6ab9a05bfb6f/bf5ae/gatsby-remark-vscode__js.webp 1405w\"\n              sizes=\"(max-width: 1405px) 100vw, 1405px\"\n              type=\"image/webp\"\n            />\n          <source\n            srcset=\"/static/cfbed43c12c620eeb99d6ab9a05bfb6f/01e7c/gatsby-remark-vscode__js.png 512w,\n/static/cfbed43c12c620eeb99d6ab9a05bfb6f/2bef9/gatsby-remark-vscode__js.png 1024w,\n/static/cfbed43c12c620eeb99d6ab9a05bfb6f/b30aa/gatsby-remark-vscode__js.png 1405w\"\n            sizes=\"(max-width: 1405px) 100vw, 1405px\"\n            type=\"image/png\"\n          />\n          <img\n            class=\"gatsby-resp-image-image\"\n            src=\"/static/cfbed43c12c620eeb99d6ab9a05bfb6f/b30aa/gatsby-remark-vscode__js.png\"\n            alt=\"Gatsby Remark VS Code (JavaScript preview)\"\n            title=\"Gatsby Remark VS Code (JavaScript preview)\"\n            loading=\"lazy\"\n            decoding=\"async\"\n            style=\"width:100%;height:100%;margin:0;vertical-align:middle;position:absolute;top:0;left:0;\"\n          />\n        </picture>\n  </a>\n    </span></p>\n<p>You can <a href=\"https://www.gatsbyjs.com/plugins/gatsby-remark-vscode/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener\">read more about the gatsby-remark-vscode plugin here</a>.</p>\n<style class=\"grvsc-styles\">\n  .grvsc-container {\n    overflow: auto;\n    position: relative;\n    -webkit-overflow-scrolling: touch;\n    padding-top: 1rem;\n    padding-top: var(--grvsc-padding-top, var(--grvsc-padding-v, 1rem));\n    padding-bottom: 1rem;\n    padding-bottom: var(--grvsc-padding-bottom, var(--grvsc-padding-v, 1rem));\n    border-radius: 8px;\n    border-radius: var(--grvsc-border-radius, 8px);\n    font-feature-settings: normal;\n    line-height: 1.4;\n  }\n  \n  .grvsc-code {\n    display: table;\n  }\n  \n  .grvsc-line {\n    display: table-row;\n    box-sizing: border-box;\n    width: 100%;\n    position: relative;\n  }\n  \n  .grvsc-line > * {\n    position: relative;\n  }\n  \n  .grvsc-gutter-pad {\n    display: table-cell;\n    padding-left: 0.75rem;\n    padding-left: calc(var(--grvsc-padding-left, var(--grvsc-padding-h, 1.5rem)) / 2);\n  }\n  \n  .grvsc-gutter {\n    display: table-cell;\n    -webkit-user-select: none;\n    -moz-user-select: none;\n    user-select: none;\n  }\n  \n  .grvsc-gutter::before {\n    content: attr(data-content);\n  }\n  \n  .grvsc-source {\n    display: table-cell;\n    padding-left: 1.5rem;\n    padding-left: var(--grvsc-padding-left, var(--grvsc-padding-h, 1.5rem));\n    padding-right: 1.5rem;\n    padding-right: var(--grvsc-padding-right, var(--grvsc-padding-h, 1.5rem));\n  }\n  \n  .grvsc-source:empty::after {\n    content: ' ';\n    -webkit-user-select: none;\n    -moz-user-select: none;\n    user-select: none;\n  }\n  \n  .grvsc-gutter + .grvsc-source {\n    padding-left: 0.75rem;\n    padding-left: calc(var(--grvsc-padding-left, var(--grvsc-padding-h, 1.5rem)) / 2);\n  }\n  \n  /* Line transformer styles */\n  \n  .grvsc-has-line-highlighting > .grvsc-code > .grvsc-line::before {\n    content: ' ';\n    position: absolute;\n    width: 100%;\n  }\n  \n  .grvsc-line-diff-add::before {\n    background-color: var(--grvsc-line-diff-add-background-color, rgba(0, 255, 60, 0.2));\n  }\n  \n  .grvsc-line-diff-del::before {\n    background-color: var(--grvsc-line-diff-del-background-color, rgba(255, 0, 20, 0.2));\n  }\n  \n  .grvsc-line-number {\n    padding: 0 2px;\n    text-align: right;\n    opacity: 0.7;\n  }\n  \n</style>","frontmatter":{"date":"March 25, 2022","title":"My Gatsby Markdown Code Highlighting of Choice and Why\n","description":"Find out on this post which code highlighting I am using on the design-code.tips website and why.\n","tags":["Gatsby","Performance","Web Development"]}}},"pageContext":{"id":"40a05ce8-e6c4-5dd5-8bf9-67d888004c5f"}},
